Introduction
------------

coZeroconf is cozybit's zeroconf stack.  It's a suite of software that allows a
user to:

-- Acquire an IP address in the event that no DHCP server is available
-- Resolve names to IP addresses
-- Advertise available services

Building
--------

$ make -C mDNS

Releasing
---------

$ ./scripts/release.sh

If a new release version is desired:

$ ./scripts/release.sh -n 1.23
Note that this will create a new Git release tag of the format v1.23
